name: AT-ST Dual Cannon
Lore: 'High rate of fire used for anti-personnel operations. Enhanced design from prototype used in the Battle of Hoth.',
Text: 'Use 1 Force to deploy on your AT-ST. May target a character, creature or vehicle for 1 Force. Draw destiny. Add 1 if targeting a character or creature. Target hit if total destiny > defense value. May fire repeatedly for 2 Force each time.',
